  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageSerializer
    Deprecated. 
    As of release 3.2.6, not directly replaced - supported through HaltedTraverserStrategy.

    @Deprecated
public class GryoLiteMessageSerializerV1d0
extends AbstractGryoMessageSerializerV1d0
    An alternative Gryo serializer that uses "referenced" graph elements during serialization. Referenced elements such as ReferenceVertex exclude the label and the properties associated with it and only return the identifier.
    Author:
    Stephen Mallette (http://stephen.genoprime.com)
